# Nexus virtual care / telehealth encounter provider mode.
# Supported values: local, external_url, daily, zoom.
# local keeps packets in the Nexus provider review queue only.
# external_url prepares a handoff to an intake URL but does not claim a visit was created.
# daily can create a Daily video room only after consent and confirmation.
# zoom is credential-detected and execution-gated until the Zoom adapter passes provider QA.
